title: Credits
go-to: force_new_page_credits

@force_new_page_credits
new-page: true

This game was developed by <a class="link" href="https://www.reddit.com/user/_BrokenArrows/">u/_BrokenArrows</a>. It is a fork from the Autumn Chen's <a class="link" href="https://red-autumn.itch.io/petrograd-1917">Petrograd 1917</a>, the prequel to the amazing original, <a class="link" href="https://red-autumn.itch.io/social-democracy">Social Democracy, an Alternate History</a>.  If you have not tried them out you should! Immediately!

Added to that, the acclaimed mod to that game by originn0, <a class="link" href="https://originn0.github.io/dynamic_social_democracy/">Dynamic Social Democracy</a>, was invaluable in making this game and all the coding tricks that it uses.

Peak, fork, and play around with the code from <a class="link" href="https://github.com/broken-arrows/route_to_itaca">GitHub</a>. Just as in the originals, many works were referenced in the making of this game.

